Package: tasktrackercli
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Talleyrand <blanchot@et.esiea.fr>
Description: A modern C++ command-line task manager using CLI11, fmt, and nlohmann_json.
 This lightweight CLI tool allows users to add, edit, delete, and view tasks
 with status tracking (todo, in-progress, done). Task data is stored in a local JSON file.
Homepage: https://github.com/LeMarechalDeFer/TaskTracker
